About this item

  • 【Great Value Package】Snow Flocked Christmas Tree have the effect of a thick snow colored flocking,Flocked Snow Tree with Pine Cones and 700 tips measure in 6 feet (1.8m) tall,it is high enough to give the tree a wonderful full look.
  • 【Simple Assembly】To finish the assembly of this 6ft Christmas tree requires only a few steps, after putting branches and metal stand together, you need to expand the branches of the whole Christmas tree. When you open all the branches, you will find that it will become a very beautiful Christmas tree.
  • LASTING DURABILITY : Built to endure many holidays with its sturdy metal base, our time-tested needles are also fire resistant and non-allergenic.Our Snowy Christmas Tree tips are Fire Retardant and made from 100% Virgin PVC helping you rest with ease this Christmas
  • 【Creativity On The Branch】Christmas Tree Snow effect is so stable.With a little creative of you own,you can hang some decorations or gifts on the branches.That's sure to catch the attention of your family and friend.
  • 【Natural Lifelike Appeal】We carefully designed the Snow Christmas tree to make it full of natural colors.You can feel near the truth tree, the pine cone, the branches and the leaves,adds rustic charm to your living room. Natural and realistic appearance makes the Christmas tree stand out.

Product Description

Read more

Flocked Christmas Tree have the effect of a thick snow colored flocking,Flocked Snow Tree with Pine Cones with 700 tips measure in 6 feet (1.8m) tall,it is high enough to give the tree a wonderful full look.

6FT

Flocked Christmas Tree have the effect of a thick snow colored flocking,Flocked Snow Tree with 700 tips measure in 6 feet (1.8m) tall,it is high enough to give the tree a wonderful full look.

TREE SECTION

The Artificial Xmas tree can be separate into three hinged parts with a sturdy metal tree base.

EASY TO SETUP

Each Artificial Christmas tree comes with detailed assembly instructions, so you don't worry about finding any trouble whilst putting up your Christmas decorations.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
